Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like another scorcher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's summer,\Nyet you're all bundled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NThat paper's three days old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this time a middle-aged couple\Nin Verden was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the killer is a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... You said you're going\Nto Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know if I can\Nmeet up with him or not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.99,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}The Girl and the Seasoned Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:56.07,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Giessen Police Station\N(Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,110,,You got your start\Nin the French Foreign Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After going off on your own, you joined\Nthe fighting in Nicaragua in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1981 to 1984 you aided\Nthe Afghan rebel guerillas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1987, you played a central role\Nin the Mossad's secret operation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to assassinate Islamic extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a brilliant fighting record,\NHugo Bernhardt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Since a mercenary such as you\Nis sponsoring this seminar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must have some\Noutstanding students graduating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a good idea to send\Nour young ones to attend your lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and have you whip them into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this man outstanding?\NI believe he showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at your training grounds\Nabout five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He is brilliant with a scalpel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but did he show an aptitude\Nwith a pistol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no wish to speak\Nabout my students...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.85,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Five Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever learned\Nto shoot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're self-taught...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shot a gun before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I know I'm asking\Nfor the impossible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice\Nbut to ask you for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, anyone\Nwho comes here is asked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to forget all he's learned about guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had anyone\Nwho'd never shot a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of your experience,\Nthis is where everyone starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your balance! Your balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't do it as well as you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always keep an eye\Non the trainees for the trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, you needn't glare at me\Nthat way. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a brambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's looking for food\Nfor its chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so exhausted that\Nyou've lost your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating is part of your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she your child... or, your grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That child's mother\Nwas shot and killed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before her eyes... in Myanmar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I ran into a hut in the jungles\Nfor shelter, they were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother was holding a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd been a fraction\Nof a second slower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have been shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why\NI brought that child here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she began living with me,\Nthat child has never smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably die hating me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have a gun,\Nthat sort of thing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you're better off\Nnever picking up a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells nice...\NIt smells like daphne blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for some running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done running,\Ncome to the low ground in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Low ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Firing range...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you shoot your gun,\Npull the trigger twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By pulling the trigger twice,\Nyou raise the probability
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll get your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that,\Nconsider yourself dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always preparing meals for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so today I decided to make you\Nsome Japanese food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called {\i1}nikujaga{\i0}.\NI hope you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are chopsticks.\NThey're carved out of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they would enhance\Nthe Japanese feel of the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You use those chopsticks well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a brambling chick.\NI guess it fell out of its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to return it to its nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick is going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult to raise it\Naway from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare that you\Ncan do it successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return it to its nest...\Nto its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is determined\Nin three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's even an instant of hesitation,\Nthe one killed will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How was his performance record\Nwhen he finished the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, he had a perfect score,\Nand his physical condition also improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,His concentration\Nwas phenomenal. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to shoot a person\Nis another issue altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's able to shoot\Nhis first person will determine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whether he will or won't be able to\Nuse his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I wonder which way he'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind about that.\NDo you have any idea where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell me if you do know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for everything,\Nthese five months...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enclosed is the rest of my tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And please help yourself\Nto the nikujaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have my sincere thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? You do know where\Nhe went, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine... You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
